!Atajos de teclado para mac

Vía: [http://www.stumbleupon.com/su/1oRufR/www.usingmac.com/2007/11/21/mac-os-x-leopard-200-productivity-booster-hotkeys/r:f]
y algunos que he ido añadiendo.

!Generales
* **Cmd-C** 	Copy files
* **Cmd-V** 	Paste files
* **Option-Drag** 	Copy files to new location
* **Cmd-Drag** 	Move and auto-align icons
* **Cmd-Delete** 	Delete
* **Cmd-Option-Drag** 	Make alias
* **Cmd-Shift-Delete** 	Empty trash
* **Cmd-Shift-Option-Delete** 	Empty trash without warning
* **Tab** 	Select next field
* **Shift-Tab** 	Select previous field
* **Return** 	Perform default action
* **Escape** 	Close dialog box
* **Page Up** 	Scroll up list
* **Up Arrow** 	Select item above
* **Page Down** 	Scroll down list
* **Down Arrow** 	Select item below
* **Cmd-Shift-G** 	Open \'Go to Folder\' dialog
* **Cmd-Period[.]** 	Close dialog box
* **Ctrl-Shift-Eject** 	Apaga la pantalla
* **Ctrl-Eject** 	Muestra el diálogo apagar equipo
!Exposé, Space, Dashboard y el sistema

* **F8** 	Toggle Space
* **Shift-F8** 	Toggle Space in slow motion
* **F9** 	Show all open windows
* **Shift-F9** 	Show all open windows in slow motion
* **F10** 	Show all open windows for an application
* **Shift-F10** 	Show all open windows for an application in slow motion
* **F11** 	Hide all windows
* **Shift-F11** 	Hide all windows in slow motion
* **F12** 	Open/close Dashboard
* **Shift-F12** 	Slowly open/close Dashboard
* **Option-Mouse Hover** 	Reveal the close button of widget
* **Shift-Click Close Button** 	Animate closing widget in slow motion
* **Cmd-H** 	Hide application
* **Cmd-Option-H** 	Hide other applications
* **Cmd-Q** 	Quit application
* **Cmd-Shift-Q** 	Quit all applications and log out
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-Q** 	Log out without warning
* **Cmd-Tab** 	Switch to next application
* **Cmd-Shift-Tab** 	Switch to previous application
* **Option-Drag** 	Adjust volume (on sound volume slider)
* **Cmd-Drag** 	Arrange menu bar items
* **Option-Click** 	Switch window and hide current window
* **Control-Click** 	Open contextual menu
* **Cmd-Control-D** 	See word definition (with mouse hover)

!Cuelges, apagados y reinicio

* **Cmd-Period[.]** 	Stop process
* **Cmd-Option-Escape** 	Open Force Quit
* **Power Key** 	Turn off
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-Power Key** 	Force shut down
* **Cmd-Control-Power Key** 	Force restart
* **Cmd+Ctrl+Option+Eject** Apaga el equipo sin que salga la ventana de confirmar.

!Acceso completo mediante teclado

* **Control-F1** 	Turn on/off full keyboard access
* **Control-F2** 	Focusing menu bar
* **Control-F3** 	Focusing Dock
* **Control-F4** 	Move to next window
* **Control-F5** 	Move to toolbar
* **Control-F6** 	Move to a floating window
* **Control-F7** 	Toggle keyboard access mode
* **Control-F8v 	Focusing status menu in menu bar
* **Cmd-Accent[`]** 	Switch to next window within application
* **Cmd-Shift-Accent[`]** 	Switch to previous window within application
* **Cmd-Option-Accent[`]** 	Move to sidebar
* **Cmd-Option-T** 	Toggle on/off character palette
!Finder

* **Cmd-Click on Title** 	See the path enclosing folders
* **Cmd-Double-Click (on folder)** 	Open folder in new window
* **Option-Double-Click (on folder)** 	Open folder in new window and close current window
* **Cmd-1** 	Switch to icon view
* **Cmd-2** 	Switch to list view
* **Cmd-Option-Right Arrow** 	Expand folder
* **Cmd-Left Arrow** 	Close folder
* **Cmd-Down Arrow** 	Open selected folder
* **Cmd-Option-Down Arrow **	Open selected folder in new window and close current folder
* **Cmd-Shift-Option-Down Arrow** 	Open selected folder in new window and close current folder in slow motion
* **Cmd-Up Arrow** 	Show enclosing folder
* **Cmd-Option-Up Arrow** 	Show enclosing folder and close current folder
* **Cmd-3** 	Switch to column view
* **Cmd-4** 	Switch to coverflow view
* **Cmd-Y** 	Toggle Quick Look mode
* **Cmd-Option-Y** 	Toggle Slideshow mode
* **Cmd-Shift-H** 	Open home folder
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-Up** Arrow 	Move focus to Desktop
* **Cmd-Shift-I** 	Open iDisk
* **Cmd-Shift-D** 	Open Desktop
* **Cmd-Shift-C** 	Open Computer area
* **Cmd-Shift-K** 	Open Network
* **Cmd-Shift-A** 	Open Applications
* **Double-Click on Title** 	Minimize window
* **Cmd-M** 	Minimize window
* **Option-Click on button** 	Apply action to all windows in active application
* **Hold-Scroll Bar** 	Scroll quickly

!Búsquedas: Spotlight

* **Cmd-Spacebar** 	Activate/deactivate Spotlight
* **Cmd-Option-Spacebar** 	Open Spotlight window
* **Cmd-Return** 	Open the top hit
* **Cmd-Down Arrow** 	Move to next category
* **Cmd-Up Arrow** 	Move to previous category
* **Cmd-Click** 	Open selected item in Finder
* **Escape** 	Close Spotlight

!Utilidades: Imprimir pantalla

* **Cmd-Shift-3** 	Take snapshot of the whole screen
* **Cmd-Shift-4** 	Take snapshot of the selected area
* **Cmd-Shift-4-Spacebar** 	Take picture of a window
* **Escape** 	Cancel
* **Hold Spacebar after Drawing the region** 	Move the selected area
* **Hold Option** 	Resize selected area
* **Hold Shift** 	Resize selected area horizontally or vertically

!Aplicación: Dock

* **Drag the separator** 	Resize Dock
* **Option-Drag** 	Resize Dock to fixed size
* **Control-Click** 	Show Dock\'s contextual menu
* **Control-Click on icon** 	Show item\'s contextual menu
* **Cmd-Click** 	Open the icon\'s enclosing folder
* **Option-Click** 	Switch to another and hide current application
* **Cmd-Option-Click** 	Switch to another application and hide all other applications
* **Cmd-Option-Drop** 	Force application to open files
* **Cmd-Option-D** 	Hide/unhide Dock

!Preferencias: Acceso Universal

* **Cmd-Option-8** 	Turn zoom on/off
* **Cmd-Option-Equal[=]** 	Zoom in
* **Control-Scroll Up** 	Zoom in
* **Cmd-Option-Hyphen[-]** 	Zoom out
* **Control-Scroll Down** 	Zoom out
* **Cmd-Option-Control-8** 	Invert color (try this on those iMacs in Apple Store)
* **Control-Option-Cmd-Comma[,]** 	Reduce contrast
* **Control-Option-Cmd-Period[.]** 	Increase contrast
* **Cmd-F5** 	Toggle VoiceOver
* **Shift-Shift-Shift-Shift-Shift (5 times)** 	Toggle Sticky Keys
* **Option-Option-Option-Option-Option (5 times)** 	Toggle mouse keys

!Arranque

Estos atajos sólo están disponibles en el arranque de la máquina.
* **Shift** 	Prevent automatic login
* **Shift** 	Enter safe mode (hold down after startup tone and release after you see the progress indicator)
* **Shift** 	Prevent opening Login Items (after login)
* **C** 	Boot from CD
* **N** 	Boot from default NetBook disk
* **T** 	Start up in Target Disk Mode
* **Option** 	Select startup disk
* **Cmd-X** 	Start up using Mac OS X
* **Hold Mouse Button** 	Eject removable discs
* **Cmd-Option-P-R** 	Reset parameter RAM
* **Cmd-V** 	Verbose mode (detailed status message)
* **Cmd-S** 	Single user mode

!Navegador: Safari

* **Cmd-Option-F** 	Move to Google Search Box
* **Option-Up Arrow** 	Scroll Up
* **Option-Down Arrow** 	Scroll Down
* **Cmd-Click Link** 	Open in new tab and stay in current tab
* **Cmd-Shift-Click Link** 	Open and go to new tab
* **Cmd-Option-Click Link** 	Open in new window
* **Option-Click Close Button** 	Close other tabs
* **Cmd-Shift-]** 	Select next tab
* **Cmd-Shift-[** 	Select previous tab
* **Cmd-Shift-H** 	Go to homepage
* **Cmd-Shift-K**	Toggle Block Pop-up Windows
* **Cmd-Option-E** 	Empty Cache
* **Cmd-Option-R** 	Reload page without Caching
* **Cmd-F** 	Search term in webpage
* **Cmd-M** 	Minimize Safari
* **Shift-Click Button** 	Animate slow motion effect
* **Cmd-Plus[+]** 	Increase font size
* **Cmd-Hyphen[-]** 	Reduce font size
* **Cmd-0** 	Original font size

!Música: iTunes

* **Return/Space** 	Play
* **Option-Right Arrow** 	Select next album
* **Option-Left Arrow** 	Select previous album
* **Cmd-Right Arrow** 	Play next song
* **Cmd-Left Arrow** 	Play previous song
* **Option-Click on Shuffle Button** 	Reshuffle
* **Cmd-Option-Down Arrow** 	Mute
* **Cmd-E** 	Eject CD
* **Cmd-T** 	Turn on/off visualizer
* **Cmd-F** 	Turn on/off full screen mode
* **Cmd-1** 	View iTunes window
* **Cmd-2** 	View equalizer mode

!Terminal

* **Double-Click** 	Select word
* **Triple-Click** 	Select line
* **Drag item to Terminal** 	Add the complete path to that item
* **Cmd-N** 	Create new shell window
* **Cmd-Shift-N** 	Enter new command
* **Cmd-Shift-K** 	Connect to a server
* **Cmd-Option-S** 	Save text
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-S** 	Save selected text
* **Cmd-I** 	Show terminal inspector
* **Cmd-T** 	Create new tab
* **Control-C** 	Break

!Mail

* **Cmd-N** 	New message
* **Cmd-Shift-N** 	Get new mail
* **Cmd-Option-N** 	Open new viewer window
* **Cmd-0** 	Open activity window
* **Cmd-Shift-Y** 	Add senders to address book
* **Cmd-E** 	Use selected text to find
* **Cmd-C while selecting message** 	Copy entire text of a message
* **Cmd-Click on upper-right corner toolbar button** 	Switch different toolbar display
* **Cmd-Single Quote[\']** 	Increase quote level
* **Cmd-Option-Single Quote[\']** 	Decrease quote level
* **Cmd-Shift-E** 	Redirect message
* **Cmd-Shift-F** 	Forward message
* **Hold Option when deleting message** 	Prevent next message from being automatically marked as read
* **Cmd-Shift-R** 	Reply to all
* **Cmd-Shift-B** 	Bounce to sender
* **Cmd-Shift-T** 	Convert message to rich text or plain text
* **Cmd-Left Brace[{]** 	Align left
* **Cmd-Vertical Bar[|]** 	Align center
* **Cmd-Right Brace[}]** 	Align right
* **Cmd-Colon[:]** 	Check spelling
* **Cmd-Semicolon[;]** 	Flag misspelling of selected word

!Front Row

* **Cmd-Esc** 	Open/close Front Row or return to previous menu
* **Spacebar, Return** 	Select item in a menu
* **Up Arrow, Down Arrow** 	Change volume
* **Right Arrow, Left Arrow** 	Go to next or previous selection

!Agenda

* **Cmd-1** 	View card and columns
* **Cmd-2** 	View only card
* **Cmd-3** 	View directories
* **Cmd-Right Bracket[\']\']** 	Next card
* **Cmd-Left Bracker[\'[\']** 	Previous card
* **Cmd-Vertical Line[|]** 	Merge selected cards
* **Cmd-Backslash[\\]** 	Set as company card

!Adobe Photoshop

* **Cmd-Shift-M** 	Edit in ImageReady
* **Cmd-Option-W** 	Close all
* **Cmd-Option-S** 	Save as
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-S** 	Save for Web
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-I** 	File info
* **Cmd-Option-P** 	Print with Preview
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-P** 	Print one copy
* **Cmd-Shift-F** 	Fade
* **Cmd-Shift-C** 	Copy merged
* **Cmd-Shift-V** 	Paste into
* **Shift-F5** 	Fill with color
* **Cmd-Shift-T** 	Transform Again
* **Cmd-Option-Shift-K** 	Show keyboard shortcuts
* **Cmd-L** 	Adjust levels
* **Cmd-M** 	Adjust curves
* **Cmd-B** 	Adjust color balance
* **Cmd-U** 	Adjust hue/saturation
* **Cmd-Option-C** 	Change canvas size
* **Cmd-Shift-N** 	Create new layer
* **Cmd-J** 	Layer via copy
* **Cmd-Shift-J** 	Layer via cut
* **Cmd-Option-G** 	Create/release clipping mask
* **Cmd-G** 	Group layers
* **Cmd-Shift-E** 	Merge visible
* **Cmd-Shift-I** 	Select inverse
* **Cmd-Option-A** 	Select all layers
* **Shift-F6** 	Select feather (Cmd-Option-D has been assigned to hide Dock)
* **Cmd-Option-V** 	Filter vanishing point
* **Cmd-Plus[+]** 	Zoom in
* **Cmd-0** 	Fit on screen
* **Cmd-Option-0** 	Display actual pixels
* **Cmd-Single Quote[\']** 	Show grid
* **Cmd-Semicolon[;]** 	Show guides
* **Cmd-R** 	Show rulers
